            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut your<strong> red chilli[es] </strong>in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>black beans</strong></p><p>Heat a pot with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1655205352059-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1655205352059-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1655205352059-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1655205352059-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
