          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1655205365762-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>smashed avocado </strong>to the <strong>quick-pickled shallot </strong>with the <strong>remaining chopped chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and mash with a fork until smooth – this is your <strong>homemade guacamole</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1655205377829-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1655205377829-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
