            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1655205389055-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>tortillas</strong> to a plate and pop them in the <strong>microwave </strong>for 1-2 min, or until warmed through</p><p>Finely grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves </strong>from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1655205403536-x200.jpg",
