          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Load up the <strong>warmed tortillas </strong>with the <strong>homemade guacamole</strong>, <strong>spiced peppers </strong>and <strong>spicy black beans</strong></p><p>Top with <strong>grated cheese </strong>and <strong>charred mango</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>chopped mint</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
